Source: poly-tc8-profile-media-player
Section: metapackages
Priority: optional
Maintainer: OpenPolycom <apt@openpolycom.cc>
Build-Depends: debhelper-compat (= 13)
Standards-Version: 4.6.2

Package: poly-tc8-profile-media-player
Architecture: all
Depends: ${misc:Depends}, poly-app-kodi
Description: TC8 device profile: Kodi media player
 Metapackage selecting the media-player role for the Polycom TC8 panel:
 Kodi fullscreen on GBM/KMS with the board's ALSA routing and Kodi's
 default landscape skin. The config blob's PROFILE=media-player selects
 the kodi engine in the kiosk weston stack (KIOSK_ENGINE=kodi).
